videos.headline: LeBron says Cavs' Game 7 experience was huge

videos.description: Lance Stephenson acknowledges he's played a lot against LeBron James, but feels this was his best chance to knock LeBron out of the playoffs.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lance says this was his best chance against Cavs) 2018/4/29

videos.headline: Lance says this was his best chance against Cavs

videos.description: Victor Oladipo says he strives to play at the level LeBron James is at and adds that basketball is his life and he can't take a break.

videos.headline: Oladipo: 'I don't know how to take time off'

videos.description: LeBron James doesn't want to answer a question about the Raptors, saying he'll think about Toronto tomorrow.
videos.headline: LeBron says he's 'burnt' and 'tired'

videos.description: Tristan Thompson is mesmerized by what LeBron James is still able to do in his 15th season.
